  - symbols, strings, numbers, booleans, nil, keywords
  - arithmetic and inequality operators
  - recursive expressions
- proper lisp expression formatting with indentation
- package.json for formula validation
- __version__ attribute in package root
- cache initial_revdate display

### Changed
- history slider fixed for newer dash api
- switched from pygments lexer for consistent coloration
- replaced expanded formula view with depth-based representation
- improved formula grouping by level with immediate queries
- enhanced cache status coherency
- better handling of string series
- upgraded dependencies (especially flask for security)

### Fixed
- nas handling without bounds in editor
- internal and normal metadata fetching
- meta filter for key/value combos
- formula parser support for ** (exponent) operator
- packed/list type handling in spec parser
- error messaging improvements

### Removed
- rename view (functionality moved to tsinfo)
- components section from tsinfo
- supervision status hack (replaced with proper series type)
- remnants of expanded_formula in groupinfo
- tachyons css references

