## [0.11.0] - 2020-07-02

### Added
- comprehensive time series info page showing metadata, formulas, history, and plots
- catalog/search page with advanced filtering capabilities
  - filter by name (space-separated terms)
  - filter by series kind (primary/formula)
  - filter by source
  - filter by formula contents
  - filter by metadata keys/values
- complete rewrite of formula editor with elm-based graphical interface
  - formula parsing and validation
  - ace editor integration
  - live preview with plot
  - save/load functionality
- metadata editing capabilities in info page
- slider for viewing different series versions
- debouncing for search filters and plot updates
- handler option to tsh view command
- links between related views (info, editor, history)

### Changed
- upgraded to elm 0.19.1
- formula editor now required dependency (no longer optional)
- improved error handling and display across all views
- better catalog handling with lazy rendering
- metadata display separated into standard and user sections
- formula components shown as tree structure
- adapted to werkzeug 1.0 changes

### Fixed
- negative number parsing in formulas
- formula json loading on get api
- metadata value decoding for list types
- base url handling with intermediate segments
- pandas 1 compatibility

### Removed
- legacy formula editor from 0.9.0 (replaced with elm-based version)
- unnecessary debug logging

